# Test Files

- `describe(productName, () => { ... })` - usar `productName` de `@/data/global.data`
- `it('[CT-NN] - Descrição do cenário', async () => { ... })`
- Padrão AAA: `/** Arrange */`, `/** Act */`, `/** Assert */`
- Arrange: builders, data (ctNN()), signup/account
- Act: flows ou actions
- Assert: questions (whatIs*, is*), business (validação via API)
- Allure: `allure.addFeature()`, `allure.addSeverity()`, `allure.addTag()`, `allure.addLink()`
- Organizar em `tests/[feature]/[CT-NN].test.ts` ou `tests/[feature]/[subfeature]/CT-NN.test.ts`
